on building organizational structures.

54:23.000 --> 54:24.000
In order to improve

54:25.000 --> 54:26.000
the coordination of types of activities,

54:27.000 --> 54:28.000
many organizations

54:29.000 --> 54:30.000
actively use horizontal communications,

54:31.000 --> 54:32.000
