54:39.000 --> 54:40.000
Teams have become the bricks

54:41.000 --> 54:42.000
from which many modern organizations

54:43.000 --> 54:44.000
are built.

54:45.000 --> 54:46.000
Team members

54:47.000 --> 54:48.000
jointly work on the fulfillment

54:49.000 --> 54:50.000
of the same tasks.

54:51.000 --> 54:52.000
The results obtained

54:53.000 --> 54:54.000
and the degree of satisfaction

54:55.000 --> 54:56.000
from the work

54:57.000 --> 54:58.000
depend on the communication structure.

54:59.000 --> 55:00.000
In some cases,

55:01.000 --> 55:02.000
the team members

55:03.000 --> 55:04.000
work on the fulfillment

55:05.000 --> 55:06.000
of tasks side by side

55:07.000 --> 55:08.000
and which are characterized

55:09.000 --> 55:10.000
by coordination of activities.

55:11.000 --> 55:12.000
