55:19.000 --> 55:20.000
carry out direct communications

55:21.000 --> 55:22.000
with each other

55:23.000 --> 55:24.000
and freely exchange information.

55:25.000 --> 55:26.000
Sometimes such a group,

55:27.000 --> 55:28.000
such a structure

55:29.000 --> 55:30.000
is called a general channel

55:31.000 --> 55:32.000
or a communication network

55:33.000 --> 55:34.000
of the type of a star.

55:35.000 --> 55:36.000
It works best

55:37.000 --> 55:38.000
in the case of complex

55:39.000 --> 55:40.000
and non-standard tasks.

55:41.000 --> 55:42.000
Such a structure, as a rule,

